data.description: ASSUMABLE!! Assume the payoff amount at 4.5% and take a 2nd mortgage for the difference on this completely renovated home featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, LVP flooring throughout, barnyard door entrance into formal dining room and so much more. Additional amenities include new bathroom vanities, mirrors, light fixtures, ceiling fans, screened patio, outside storage shed, 2 car garage all located on approximately 1 acre. Kitchen has plenty of cabinet space and countertop space with an island to prep and prepare meals. Wood burning fireplace and staircase has been refinished to provide a contemporary style. There is also a large unfinished bonus room upstairs that would be ideal for a man's cave and a secondary bonus area that could be used as office space, library, or children play room.
